I really like everything past the description, it’s a nice creepy little story with a really good event log (love the slow realization that there is no bio relationship between the “daughter” and the parents). However the containment procedures and the description don’t feel fully developed(even with the in universe WIP), mainly because the “parents” connection to the weirdness isn’t mentioned at all. But then again that could ruin the build up to the event. Either way feels a bit underdeveloped so 8/10 event log 4/10 containment/description. I feel that even with the lacking start the end more then makes up for it! +1







